
## [HOME](scrolls/home)

# hostmedia
  
 - self-replicating set of media files
 - QR code to directly download media over wifi
 - text documents, word and pdf
 - sound files
 - videos
 - embed in scrolls, put up links and qr codes on local pages
 - flags point to domains which point to local ip addresses
 - domains also have maps which direct you to the physical wifi network
 - do this in LA and NYC as an exclusive media distribution system  
